## 4. PRIVACY & SECURITY (POPIA)

- Health data is special personal information: minimise, separate, encrypt, log access.
- Keep personal/health data IN-REGION. NEVER send identifiable patient data to offshore models.
- AI operates on MOLECULE content, not personal data.
- No secrets in code/repo. Validate input. Rate-limit AI endpoints.
